Landing page is used for advertising
and marketing purpose.
In this we can learn create coloum, divide section etc.

code with HTML
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Landing Page</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css">
</head>
<body>

  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Welcome to [Product Name]</h1>
      <p>Transform your experience with our innovative solution.</p>
      <a href="#cta" class="btn">Get Started</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Benefits Section -->
  <section id="benefits" class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Why Choose Us?</h2>
      <div class="benefit">
        <h3>Benefit 1</h3>
        <p>Describe the benefit here. What makes your product or service unique and valuable.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="benefit">
        <h3>Benefit 2</h3>
        <p>Explain another great aspect of your product that addresses customer needs.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="benefit">
        <h3>Benefit 3</h3>
        <p>Highlight another benefit to make the value of your offer clear.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Testimonials Section -->
  <section id="testimonials" class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>What Our Users Say</h2>
      <div class="testimonial">
        <p>"This product has changed the way I work. Highly recommended!"</p>
        <p>- User 1</p>
      </div>
      <div class="testimonial">
        <p>"I can't imagine going back to my old way of doing things. This is a game-changer!"</p>
        <p>- User 2</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Call-to-Action Section -->
  <section id="cta" class="cta">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Ready to Get Started?</h2>
      <p>Sign up now and experience the difference.</p>
      <a href="#" class="btn">Sign Up Now</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Footer -->
  <footer>
    <p>&copy; 2023 [Your Company Name]. All rights reserved.</p>
  </footer>

</body>
</html>


CODE WITH CSS

/* Reset */
* {
  margin: 0;
  padding: 0;
  box-sizing: border-box;
}

body {
  font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
  line-height: 1.6;
  color: #333;
}

/* Container */
.container {
  width: 90%;
  max-width: 1000px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  text-align: center;
}

/* Hero Section */
.hero {
  background: #4CAF50;
  color: #fff;
  padding: 100px 0;
}

.hero h1 {
  font-size: 2.5em;
}

.hero p {
  font-size: 1.2em;
  margin: 10px 0 20px;
}

.hero .btn {
  background: #333;
  color: #fff;
  padding: 10px 20px;
  text-decoration: none;
  border-radius: 5px;
}

/* Benefits Section */
.section {
  padding: 50px 0;
}

.section h2 {
  font-size: 2em;
  margin-bottom: 20px;
}

.benefit {
  background: #f4f4f4;
  padding: 20px;
  margin: 15px 0;
  border-radius: 5px;
}

/* Testimonials Section */
.testimonial {
  background: #eee;
  padding: 15px;
  margin: 10px 0;
  font-style: italic;
  border-radius: 5px;
}

/* CTA Section */
.cta {
  background: #4CAF50;
  color: #fff;
  padding: 50px 0;
}

.cta .btn {
  background: #333;
  color: #fff;
  padding: 10px 20px;
  text-decoration: none;
  border-radius: 5px;
  font-size: 1.1em;
}

/* Footer */
footer {
  text-align: center;
  padding: 10px;
  background: #333;
  color: #fff;
}

